  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Highly Customised Starship Engine",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "高度定制化的飞船驱动器",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高度客製化太空船引擎"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly-tuned version of the conventional starship <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Engine</span>. Wavefront occupancy has been pushed to the limit, creating a pulse experience that is both <span class=\"name name-stellar\">efficient</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly responsive</span>.<br><br>User is advised that <span class=\"name name-exotic\">Tritium</span> is required to charge the drive. Tritium is abundant in <span class=\"name name-commodity\">near-space asteroid fields</span>. Scan (<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPSCAN</span>) to search for <span class=\"name name-technology\">tritium-rich asteroids</span>.<br><br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> to engage Pulse Jump. Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "经过缜密调试过的传统飞船<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲驱动器</span>。接近极限的波面频率将能够提供<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高效</span>而且<span class=\"name name-stellar\">极度灵敏</span>的脉冲动力。<br><br>建议使用<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>作为驱动器燃料。<span class=\"name name-commodity\">近太空小行星带</span>中能够找到丰富的氚。扫描（<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPSCAN</span>）以搜寻<span class=\"name name-technology\">富含氚的小行星</span>。<br><br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span>将启动脉冲跃迁。在飞行时长按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>激活加速。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "經高度調整的常規太空船<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝引擎</span>。波陣面使用率已達到極限，可產生<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高效率</span>與<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高響應</span>的脈衝事件。<br><br>提醒使用者，驅動器需使用<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>充能。<span class=\"name name-commodity\">近太空的小行星帶</span>內有大量的氚。掃描 (<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPSCAN</span>) 即可找尋<span class=\"name name-technology\">富含氚的小行星</span>。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> 發動脈衝跳躍。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> 啟動飛行加速功能。"
  },
